description: **ACCEPTED OFFER OH CANCELLED** | This thoughtfully designed unit features granite countertops and stainless steel appliances that perfectly complement the hardwood floors throughout. Enjoy your own fully fenced, deeded brick patio—ideal for entertaining—just off the private rear porch. The versatile second bedroom is perfect as a home office, nursery, or guest room. Additional highlights include central air conditioning, common laundry, and private basement storage. Self-managed association with $12,000+ in reserves. Tremendous upside potential due to proximity to the 21-acre On The Dot planned development.
